{
  "name": "07 — Sync: Progresso Hotmart",
  "active": false,
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "w7-note-001",
      "name": "Nota — Configuração",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Fluxo 07 — Sincronização de Progresso (Hotmart)\n\n**Variáveis de ambiente necessárias (n8n Settings → Variables):**\n- `HOTMART_BASIC_TOKEN` — Base64 de `client_id:client_secret` (Hotmart → Ferramentas → Credenciais API)\n\n**Credencial necessária:** Supabase — jornada_alunos\n\n**Gatilho:** Cron — todo dia às 06:00 (antes do Tutor às 09:00)\n\n**Pré-requisito:** Migration 006 executada e `hotmart_product_id` preenchido nos 11 produtos.\n\n**Lógica:**\n1. Busca todos os produtos com `hotmart_product_id` definido\n2. Para cada produto: obtém access_token OAuth e consulta progresso via API Hotmart\n3. Para cada aluno retornado: calcula status_aluno pelo progresso\n4. Atualiza `aluno_produtos` (progresso_pct, ultimo_acesso) e `alunos` (status_aluno)\n5. Alunos não cadastrados no Supabase são ignorados silenciosamente\n\n**Regras de status:**\n  0% sem acesso → nunca_acessou · 0% com acesso → inativo\n  1–29% → iniciante · 30–69% → em_andamento\n  70–99% → quase_concluindo · 100% → concluido",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 2800
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-001",
      "name": "Cron — Diário 06h",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [240, 460],
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "days",
              "triggerAtHour": 6,
              "triggerAtMinute": 0
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-002",
      "name": "Supabase — Buscar Produtos Ativos",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [460, 460],
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "getAll",
        "tableId": "produtos",
        "returnAll": true
      },
      "credentials": {
        "supabaseApi": {
          "id": "SUPABASE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Supabase — jornada_alunos"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-003",
      "name": "Loop por Produto",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [680, 460],
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1,
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-004",
      "name": "Tem hotmart_product_id?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [900, 460],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "loose" },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-product-id",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.hotmart_product_id }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "notEmpty", "singleValue": true }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-005",
      "name": "Hotmart — Gerar Access Token",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1120, 320],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api-sec-vlc.hotmart.com/security/oauth/token",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Basic {{ $env.HOTMART_BASIC_TOKEN }}" }
          ]
        },
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "grant_type", "value": "client_credentials" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "failOnStatusCode": false
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-006",
      "name": "Hotmart — Buscar Progresso",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1340, 320],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "https://developers.hotmart.com/club/api/v1/pages/progress",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "Authorization", "value": "=Bearer {{ $json.access_token }}" }
          ]
        },
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            { "name": "product_id",  "value": "={{ $('Loop por Produto').item.json.hotmart_product_id }}" },
            { "name": "max_results", "value": "100" }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "failOnStatusCode": false
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-007",
      "name": "Extrair Alunos",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1560, 320],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const response = $input.first().json;\nconst items = response.items || [];\n\n// Se não há dados, retorna item sentinela para a branch FALSE de 'Tem dados?'\nif (items.length === 0) {\n  return [{ json: { subscriber_email: null, skip: true } }];\n}\n\nreturn items.map(student => ({ json: { ...student, skip: false } }));"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-008",
      "name": "Tem dados?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1780, 320],
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": { "caseSensitive": false, "leftValue": "", "typeValidation": "loose" },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "cond-tem-dados",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.subscriber_email }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": { "type": "string", "operation": "notEmpty", "singleValue": true }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-009",
      "name": "Loop por Aluno",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [2000, 180],
      "parameters": {
        "batchSize": 1,
        "options": {}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-010",
      "name": "Calcular Status",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2220, 180],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const progresso = $json.progress_percentage || 0;\nconst temAcesso = $json.last_access_date != null;\n\nlet status;\nif (progresso === 0 && !temAcesso) {\n  status = 'nunca_acessou';\n} else if (progresso === 0) {\n  status = 'inativo';\n} else if (progresso < 30) {\n  status = 'iniciante';\n} else if (progresso < 70) {\n  status = 'em_andamento';\n} else if (progresso < 100) {\n  status = 'quase_concluindo';\n} else {\n  status = 'concluido';\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    email:        $json.subscriber_email,\n    progresso_pct: Math.round(progresso),\n    ultimo_acesso: $json.last_access_date || null,\n    status_aluno:  status\n  }\n}];"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "w7-node-011",
